metadata.name: Winds of Change
metadata.description:
The image represents change towards a favorable future. It can mean progress, an improvement in one's state of mind, or a shift to a more positive disposition. "Winds of Change" was shot in Ilocos Norte, Philippines.

This comes with a 20"x35" archival print with a certificate of authenticity.

Artist name: AJ Duran
Series name: Ephemera
Edition type: 1/1 NFT
